{"tid":1141270,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"我唐仔對唔住大家","createTime":"2019-05-06T11:03:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T01:35:40.000Z","uid":211346,"like":1,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"336c676bd4fcae9ac78f3c4073e527be6feb7a2d","tid":1141270,"uid":211346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T11:03:57.000Z","msg":"我知我係你地心目中係個超級天才，絕頂聰明，但其實我科chem係未有5*。<br />\n不過你地要記住，係未有5* 。而唔係冇5*，我今年已經考過DSE chem, 今次一定有5*，我唐仔話既<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nps 你班死毒撚同我死埋一面<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7900bddaa1f8124eac92e56d032cd905fd53a455","tid":1141270,"uid":200227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T11:05:28.000Z","msg":"屌唐狗原來係用未來嚟打J<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33042d0966d6fc2b4768b23826f02a234c6f3ada","tid":1141270,"uid":210729,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T11:09:46.000Z","msg":"挑 未有5*都攞出來講 on99 <br />\n咁我都可以話自己係未做世界首富 就嚟做啦 <br />\n利申 已all in牛市"},{"pid":"7092681a6ef55c970d5e5b051f96b0eb41aacf5a","tid":1141270,"uid":21501,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T11:15:39.000Z","msg":"🦢🈹🉐🍐🔛9️⃣9️⃣"},{"pid":"217a0af87e65f13dd2484f721c2be1db48203ef2","tid":1141270,"uid":113373,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T11:34:09.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反對修訂逃犯條例 香港的終局之戰</span><br />\n<br />\n星期六 早上9點 <br />\n立法會將會開會討論有關修訂 暫未知會否表決 <br />\n由於秘書處政變 原本由涂謹申主持會議改為石禮謙主持<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">事態危急</span><br />\n一定要阻止立法<br />\n否則香港直送中國受審<br />\n到時中國話你犯咗中國法律 無需證據 無需理由<br />\n就可以光明正大係香港夾你返中國 <br />\n坐黑獄 洗你腦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">此修例禍害大於23條立法<br />\n23條&gt;&gt;&gt;(需危害國家安全，香港審判，香港監禁)<br />\n<br />\n修訂逃犯條例 &gt;&gt;&gt;(莫需有，中國政府可任意控告香港人任何罪行，香港會配合執法將你拘捕，移交中國審判及監禁，無需證據 無需理由)</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"60d42498f815aeecfa07526965cb34a2f90409e6","tid":1141270,"uid":200227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T13:23:57.000Z","msg":"原來狗入得考場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e2c78653291ec4ee7f3671f3987385b15fb747d","tid":1141270,"uid":175032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T13:26:00.000Z","msg":"收爺啦唐狗"},{"pid":"f60aca0fa8c16919542533bd255956183a82ff16","tid":1141270,"uid":184509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T13:28:24.000Z","msg":"點解唔係5**"},{"pid":"9a1e89607554f44561fe206b7cab3d68ec708adb","tid":1141270,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T13:33:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ca2a446fd6fa776be07e9ad47cf4127a0a34f96","tid":1141270,"uid":199441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T14:18:09.000Z","msg":"收手啦唐仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e035b6d998ab35adaa3f9930f3e04431a42c724a","tid":1141270,"uid":211346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33042d0966d6fc2b4768b23826f02a234c6f3ada","tid":1141270,"uid":210729,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T11:09:46.000Z","msg":"挑 未有5*都攞出來講 on99 <br />\n咁我都可以話自己係未做世界首富 就嚟做啦 <br />\n利申 已all in牛市"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T02:50:36.000Z","msg":"你都on99你又唔係做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5601c107286cd48515f85743df8b8b3d1ecbcd3a","tid":1141270,"uid":211346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7092681a6ef55c970d5e5b051f96b0eb41a